        "TileImage": "$($repository 5914df8a-1b58-43fd-8b1c-00084d4973e9).Image",
        "Description": "In the rain-soaked alleys of Chongqing, whispers of a conspiracy echo. Your mission: eliminate three key targets tied to a criminal syndicate. Each is heavily guarded and unpredictable. Use the environment, blend with the crowds, and strike with precision. The shadows are your ally, and silence your greatest weapon. Navigate the streets and complete the mission without a trace. The fate of Chongqing rests in your hands, Agent 47.",
